qas.question: In which month of 1955 was this pact declared?

context: On <b1_0>14 <a0_0>May<a0_0/> 1955<b1_0/>, the USSR and other seven European countries "reaffirming their desire for the establishment of a system of European collective security based on the participation of all European states irrespective of their social and political systems" established the <b2_0><b3_0>Warsaw<b3_0/><b2_0/> Pact in response to the integration of the <b4_0>Federal Republic of Germany<b4_0/> into NATO, declaring that: "a remilitarized Western Germany and the integration of the latter in the North-Atlantic bloc [...] increase the danger of another war and constitutes a threat to the national security of the peaceable states; [...] in these circumstances the peaceable European states must take the necessary measures to safeguard their security".
